data.description: Gorgeous 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home in beautiful Chapel Trail. Stainless steel appliances. First floor features tile floors, open eat-in kitchen, and open family/living room. Enter the large enclosed screened patio from either the kitchen or living/family room. Outside the patio is a fenced back yard perfect for kids, grilling and pets. Second floor features wood flooring in all bedrooms, spacious master bedroom and bath with ample master closet space.  Energy efficient home, equipped with accordion shutters on all windows and doors, impact garage doors, Air Conditioner 2016, Roof 2007 in amazing area with all rated A schools.Motivated sellers with a 2.7% mortgage rate assumable to qualified buyers.
